snippet.title: TGS 2023 Video: Grasp the Stars | Honkai: Star Rail
snippet.description:
Traces of things that happened, people encountered, and roads walked all leave their mark atop the lines running along a palm.
And the most important fact remains: these lines continue to stretch on.

English Voice:
Topaz — Sam Slade
